headline: Palo Alto ’well positioned as a long-term share consolidator’ says JPMorgan
summary: Investing.com -- JPMorgan upgraded Palo Alto Networks and reinstated coverage of CyberArk after a period of restriction related to Palo Alto’s planned acquisition of CyberArk, highlighting Palo Alto’s position as a cybersecurity consolidator while taking a more cautious view on CyberArk’s standalone upside.
